body: @Reyas Well, I can see the stamina part. She literally is asking for another round and they ded.
LMAO @Reyas. I was just enjoying the pwp for what it was, but a helping of salty loredump on the side is nice as well

Haha "raped", although Kensou, Bao and Chris are formidable fighters in the game, they are canonically pretty weak in these incarnations. If they were Orochi Chris, Dragon Kensou and whatever Bao was called, they could easily overpower Vanessa but in their regular forms, she stomps all three with mid diff. She literally cannot get "raped" by them, she is one of the strongest, fastest, naturally high stamina  characters in all of KoF (No cyborg, no magic). I know nobody cares, but goddamnit I learned tons of KoF lore back in the day and if I see a chance to use it, I'm damn well going to take it
